    "author_association": "NONE",
    "body": "This would be a great feature to motivate people to link their accounts.  Rather than taking things away from people who don't register, it's nice to incentivize people with features that wouldn't otherwise be possible without an account.  Would also (hopefully) encourage positive friendly interaction.  Does anyone see a feasible way to implement this?"
