    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "The forum has a built in friends list feature. In principle we could have the game client piggyback on this to show what they are doing, but there are a number of issues that would need to be resolved (e.g. how to prevent trolls from abusing this to track someone who they want to target) and a proper specification outlined.\r\n\r\nThis would also require changes to the privacy policy, as it would mean explicitly tracking what servers each player is connecting to, and sharing it with others."
